product.title: Avocado Airpods Case (1&2)
product.body_html:
These adorable Avocado cases are inspired by our plushies and are compatible with any Apple AirPods Gen 2 & 1.

Made of silicone

Made of premium silicone material which will protect your Airpods against bumps, drops, and scratches. The inside is smooth and perfect for your Airpods to sit comfortably. Easy to open and close the case, and can be disassembled effortlessly. 

Eco-Friendly

Environmental-friendly soft silicone rubber with no toxic smell. Small and robust, perfect for a strong grip yet a soft and comfortable feeling - sort of like a stress ball.

All-round protection

Shockproof, anti-scratch and anti-fingerprint material to help protect your AirPods. If our cases ever get dirty, simply clean it under warm water and soap.

3D Cute Cartoon

Our adorable range of Airpods cases is the perfect gift for yourself, your family and your friends. Unique and stylish, make your Airpods different from the rest.

Easy to carry

These Airpods Pro cases come with a ring so you don't have to worry about dropping them.

Please note the Apple AirPods do not come with our cases!
